c: 3
v: 39
t: "Then the angels called him, while he was standing in prayer in Al-Mihrab (a praying place or a private room), (saying): \"Allah gives you glad tidings of Yahya (John), confirming (believing in) the Word from Allah [i.e. the creation of 'Iesa (Jesus), the Word from Allah (\"Be!\" - and he was!)], noble, keeping away from sexual relations with women, a Prophet, from among the righteous"